Andela_assessment
----------------------------------------
This project is for the andela ALC 2.0 inermediate assessment
The project is made up of two parts 

  1. An API to perform basic CRUD operations using nodejs, Express framework and a Mysql 
    database.
  2. The webapp which consumes the API.built with nodejs, express and ejs 
  
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
To test;
1. clone this repo
2. cd into webapi
3. $ npm install 
4. $ npm intall nodemon (optional)
5. $ node server.js //to start the api 

cd into webapp and carryout the same steps 3  to 5

the webapp should be runing on http://localhost:5000/

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 link  to the  live site https://emeraldschool.herokuapp.com/
